1
00:00:29,590 --> 00:00:30,169
Thank you.

2
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:48,610
Our young lady is

3
00:00:48,610 --> 00:00:49,670
the heir of Chenghai Group.

4
00:00:50,149 --> 00:00:51,649
Her life has been

5
00:00:51,649 --> 00:00:52,909
laid out since birth.

6
00:00:53,869 --> 00:00:54,729
Your lives

7
00:00:54,990 --> 00:00:56,229
are destined not to intersect.

8
00:00:56,890 --> 00:00:57,509
Of course,

9
00:00:57,810 --> 00:00:59,210
if you have any needs,

10
00:00:59,549 --> 00:01:01,110
you can also make demands.

11
00:01:27,209 --> 00:01:29,129
Fortunately, it's a low-concentration corrosive reagent.

12
00:01:29,129 --> 00:01:30,150
The wound isn't too deep.

13
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:31,110
Change the dressing on time.

14
00:01:32,170 --> 00:01:33,950
The attacker has been taken away by the police.

15
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:35,150
He's being interrogated.

16
00:01:35,390 --> 00:01:37,150
I believe we'll get the results soon.

17
00:01:39,030 --> 00:01:39,790
Thank you.

18
00:01:44,429 --> 00:01:47,750
I always get hurt and make you worry.

19
00:01:49,790 --> 00:01:52,230
Don't take such risks in the future.

20
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:56,170
But I'm happy.

21
00:01:56,650 --> 00:01:58,269
Finally, I got a chance to save you.

22
00:01:59,429 --> 00:02:00,230
As long as it's you,

23
00:02:00,829 --> 00:02:02,129
no matter how many times I get hurt,

24
00:02:02,629 --> 00:02:03,549
it's worth it.

25
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,610
Mr. Wu, you're in a wheelchair,

26
00:02:08,969 --> 00:02:10,849
but you're so agile

27
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:12,250
to jump like that.

28
00:02:13,250 --> 00:02:15,189
The timing was just perfect.

29
00:02:16,570 --> 00:02:18,010
If it's a coincidence,

30
00:02:18,929 --> 00:02:21,170
you seem to have more coincidences

31
00:02:21,170 --> 00:02:22,309
than I do.

32
00:02:23,130 --> 00:02:24,029
Too many coincidences

33
00:02:24,369 --> 00:02:25,970
make people wonder.

34
00:02:30,209 --> 00:02:30,749
Zhou Xubai,

35
00:02:32,249 --> 00:02:33,130
come out with me.

36
00:02:48,570 --> 00:02:50,350
Is Mr. Wu Xi attacked

37
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:51,749
related to Mr. Zhou Xubai

38
00:02:51,749 --> 00:02:52,790
from Lanze Capital?

39
00:02:53,589 --> 00:02:54,890
Mr. Ye,

40
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:56,309
sorry.

41
00:02:56,610 --> 00:02:57,790
Sorry.

42
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,670
Sorry, Mr. Ye is not available for interviews now.

43
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:03,910
Mr. Ye is not available for interviews now.

44
00:03:04,049 --> 00:03:05,230
Sorry.

45
00:03:07,950 --> 00:03:09,950
Stop!

46
00:03:11,230 --> 00:03:13,089
Mr. Ye, Mr. Ye.

47
00:03:17,029 --> 00:03:18,309
Why are you here?

48
00:03:19,290 --> 00:03:20,209
The media

49
00:03:20,690 --> 00:03:22,110
are scrutinizing me and Chenghai Group.

50
00:03:22,709 --> 00:03:23,589
Your presence

51
00:03:24,089 --> 00:03:24,690
in this spotlight

52
00:03:24,890 --> 00:03:25,910
will only bring more trouble.

53
00:03:26,110 --> 00:03:26,989
So you've decided

54
00:03:27,529 --> 00:03:28,809
to stand by his side again?

55
00:03:36,970 --> 00:03:37,630
It's fine.

56
00:03:38,489 --> 00:03:39,249
I can be the one

57
00:03:39,249 --> 00:03:40,170
who remains unseen.

58
00:03:41,850 --> 00:03:42,809
As long as you need me,

59
00:03:43,290 --> 00:03:44,329
I'll always be there.

60
00:03:46,089 --> 00:03:47,470
Just don't push me away again.

61
00:03:47,730 --> 00:03:48,350
Zhou Xubai,

62
00:03:53,890 --> 00:03:54,510
there's no chance

63
00:03:56,649 --> 00:03:57,510
between us.

64
00:04:04,890 --> 00:04:05,690
So you decided

65
00:04:06,850 --> 00:04:07,709
to be with him?

66
00:04:46,650 --> 00:04:48,249
What are you trying to do?

67
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:50,150
[How do you like]

68
00:04:50,410 --> 00:04:52,530
[this big gift?]

69
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:57,569
[I've got something even bigger coming up.]

70
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:13,410
Meimei,

71
00:05:15,989 --> 00:05:17,830
you've been zoning out for half an hour.

72
00:05:19,049 --> 00:05:22,749
Jiayi, do you think I should

73
00:05:22,989 --> 00:05:24,869
I should go back to Wu Xi?

74
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:26,889
He's sacrificed so much for me,

75
00:05:27,449 --> 00:05:29,069
even nearly lost his life.

76
00:05:31,429 --> 00:05:34,230
If I follow my heart,

77
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,949
wouldn't that be too selfish?

78
00:05:36,929 --> 00:05:38,150
But you need to think clearly.

79
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:40,230
Is it love or guilt

80
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:42,150
that's driving your decision?

81
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:44,230
Mei,

82
00:05:44,230 --> 00:05:45,970
feelings can't be weighed on a scale,

83
00:05:45,970 --> 00:05:48,290
and they can't be compensated with self-sacrifice.

84
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:50,049
Close your eyes

85
00:05:50,509 --> 00:05:52,629
and try to imagine a picture.

86
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,569
At a time that makes you feel

87
00:05:54,569 --> 00:05:56,970
very safe and happy,

88
00:05:57,290 --> 00:05:59,809
you are waiting for someone to appear.

89
00:06:00,069 --> 00:06:01,389
Don't try too hard.

90
00:06:01,689 --> 00:06:03,949
Let him appear in your mind naturally.

91
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:07,249
See who he is.

92
00:07:12,509 --> 00:07:14,150
Xiaomei.

93
00:07:17,369 --> 00:07:18,530
The case has made a major breakthrough.

94
00:07:19,429 --> 00:07:20,850
The attacker has confessed

95
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:22,749
and identified the mastermind.

96
00:07:25,290 --> 00:07:25,869
Zhou Xubai.

97
00:07:33,389 --> 00:07:34,410
These are the call records

98
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:36,290
and transaction records provided by the attacker

99
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:37,129
to the police.

100
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:44,850
Make her feel threatened,

101
00:07:45,389 --> 00:07:46,309
but be discreet.

102
00:07:46,749 --> 00:07:47,869
Don't let her die.

103
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:49,110
Understood?

104
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:51,090
It's the first time I've received such a strange request.

105
00:07:51,910 --> 00:07:52,610
Boss,

106
00:07:52,989 --> 00:07:54,049
what do you want

107
00:07:54,309 --> 00:07:55,129
to get by spending so much money?

108
00:07:55,629 --> 00:07:57,270
I want her to think of me

109
00:07:57,770 --> 00:07:59,249
the only one she can think of

110
00:07:59,670 --> 00:08:00,569
when she's in panic.

111
00:08:03,090 --> 00:08:04,509
You should be familiar with his voice.

112
00:08:04,889 --> 00:08:06,470
I specifically asked a technician

113
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:07,290
to check it out.

114
00:08:07,770 --> 00:08:08,410
This voice

115
00:08:09,369 --> 00:08:10,549
is not AI synthesized.

116
00:08:13,369 --> 00:08:15,170
I want to be the only one

117
00:08:15,410 --> 00:08:16,830
she can think of

118
00:08:17,369 --> 00:08:18,470
when she's in panic.

119
00:08:21,249 --> 00:08:23,270
I want to be the only one

120
00:08:23,509 --> 00:08:24,929
she can think of

121
00:08:25,470 --> 00:08:26,309
when she is in panic.

122
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:28,970
Hello.

123
00:08:29,949 --> 00:08:30,770
Can I

124
00:08:31,590 --> 00:08:32,590
hear your voice?

125
00:08:33,889 --> 00:08:34,330
Hello.

126
00:08:34,850 --> 00:08:35,170
Hello.

127
00:08:36,309 --> 00:08:36,689
Hello.

128
00:08:37,410 --> 00:08:37,790
Hello.

129
00:08:48,989 --> 00:08:51,730
I remember it's here. Why can't I find it?

130
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:56,970
Zhi Mei.

131
00:08:57,369 --> 00:08:58,810
What are you doing?

132
00:09:02,249 --> 00:09:03,550
What are you looking for?

133
00:09:05,869 --> 00:09:08,169
Do you remember this phone?

134
00:09:08,850 --> 00:09:10,330
There are many memories of us in it.

135
00:09:10,869 --> 00:09:13,009
Unfortunately, I don't remember the password.

136
00:09:13,789 --> 00:09:14,289
Can you

137
00:09:15,070 --> 00:09:16,070
help me open it?

138
00:09:22,489 --> 00:09:23,210
It's your birthday.

139
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:24,649
How could I forget?

140
00:09:24,909 --> 00:09:25,289
Really?

141
00:09:25,830 --> 00:09:26,989
You still remember after such a long time.

142
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:28,989
The PR department said

143
00:09:29,169 --> 00:09:30,110
that after the incident

144
00:09:30,110 --> 00:09:30,950
was exposed,

145
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:32,830
the public opinion has become much more positive.

146
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:35,869
So I want to take

147
00:09:35,869 --> 00:09:36,690
this opportunity

148
00:09:36,690 --> 00:09:38,050
to arrange another exclusive interview.

149
00:09:38,749 --> 00:09:39,830
Are you willing to do it with me?

150
00:09:40,450 --> 00:09:41,389
Of course, I am.

151
00:09:42,330 --> 00:09:43,289
As long as I can be with you,

152
00:09:43,789 --> 00:09:44,509
I can do anything.
